    <item>
      <title>阿达尼和丰益国际将于下月开始出售合资企业股权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/adani-wilmar-are-said-to-start-stake-sale-in-venture-next-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，阿达尼企业有限公司 (Adani Enterprises Ltd.) 和丰益国际有限公司 (Wilmar International Ltd.) 预计将最早于下个月开始出售其消费合资企业阿达尼丰益国际有限公司 (Adani Wilmar Ltd.) 的少数股权，以遵守股权规定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/adani-wilmar-are-said-to-start-stake-sale-in-venture-next-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 09:58:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿拉比卡咖啡期货因供应担忧创下 2011 年以来新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/arabica-coffee-soars-to-most-since-2011-as-supply-woes-escalate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于持续的供应中断导致优质阿拉比卡咖啡豆的成本升至 13 年来的最高水平，一杯咖啡的价格将进一步上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/arabica-coffee-soars-to-most-since-2011-as-supply-woes-escalate</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 08:35:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿波罗与英国石油公司签署 10 亿美元协议，收购 Gas Link 股权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/apollo-reaches-1-billion-deal-with-bp-to-fund-stake-in-gas-link</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿波罗全球管理公司同意向英国石油公司支付 10 亿美元，收购里海地区一条重要天然气管道的股份，此举将有助于这家能源巨头在油价暴跌之际重新分配部分资源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/apollo-reaches-1-billion-deal-with-bp-to-fund-stake-in-gas-link</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 07:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴贾杰住房公司 (Bajaj Housing) 股价飙升 136%，创下印度大型 IPO 史上最佳首日表现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/bajaj-housing-gears-up-for-india-s-biggest-trading-debut-of-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为印度今年规模最大的新股上市交易之一，Bajaj Housing Finance Ltd. 的股价在首日交易中上涨了一倍多，反映出当地人对首次公开募股 (IPO) 的热情高涨，这继续引发人们对流动性涌入推高估值的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-16/bajaj-housing-gears-up-for-india-s-biggest-trading-debut-of-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Sep 2024 03:03:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
